{
  "stem": "107.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was what every German there believed, and what was distributed as rumor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They need thousands and thousands of laborer to make that big hole in the mountain-- in the mountains of these forests.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore they sent in whoever was able still for hard work and little food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then there were many who were too old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they stayed back in our camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know, 6,000, maybe 5,000, 7,000, including my parents, including Willie Shoenfeld, the man with whom I had-- well, he wasn't old, but he was ill.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had had tuberculosis before, and it broke out again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he big swollen glands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was obviously a sick man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "These old people were saying, I wonder what would happen, they said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then there was also the hospital still, with the patients and a couple of, four doctors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Me one of [? seven. ?] In July, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] June, July '44, the big question was what will happen with the mothers with little children, which were in one barrack.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And again, there came the orders the next morning-- we will transport some buses with little children to a special camp where they will be well taken care of.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't believe a word, but that was the official announcement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Next morning these 200, 300, [INAUDIBLE] more than 50 women with sometimes one child, sometimes two children on their hands were standing on the road waiting for what happens.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were clear what will happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But of course, nobody gives up the total hope totally that something will happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--megaphone in his hand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he announced, be clever woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Be clever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Give your children to your neighbor and come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
